Speech Recognition:
Converts spoken language into text (speech-to-text). This enables AI to understand and process voice input.

Speech Synthesis:
Converts text into spoken language (text-to-speech). Allows AI to "speak" information aloud.

Advancements in AI Speech Tech:
Modern systems handle:
- Background noise reduction
- Interruption detection
- More human-like, expressive voices

Common Use Cases for AI Speech (AI-900 Focus):
- Voice assistants (e.g., on phones, smart speakers)
- Transcription of meetings, calls, or other spoken content
- Audio narration of written content (e.g., screen readers)
- Speech translation between languages

